caller_intent: Heather Scott is attempting to confirm that the recipient (Eden) has received an email and signed an authorization form to process a payment and prevent policy cancellation.
resolution_steps: Left a voicemail message after being forwarded to an automated system.
Mentioned prior attempts to contact via email, voicemail, and text.
Requested confirmation of email receipt and authorization form signing.
Provided the office phone number for further assistance.
Expressed concern about policy cancellation and offered to help set up payment.
summary: Heather Scott from Alliance Insurance left a voicemail for Eden, following up on prior communication to ensure an authorization form was signed to process a payment and avoid policy cancellation. She provided the office number for further assistance and expressed concern about the policy's status.
